org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.externalreferences.CitedDocumentProperties
public class CitedDocumentProperties extends ExternalReferenceProperties
ExternalReferenceProperties stores information about an link to an external resource that is relevant to open metadata.
